Title: New Traveller in town
DateModified: '2018-02-21'
DatePublished: '2018-04-20'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2018/applications/new-traveller-in-town
SetInCountry: India
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Muhammad Ali Khan
AuthorCountry: India
Text: "Well, it all start with a inception, like yu meet your mom or friends after\
  \ a long time, they tell you that they have been here and there and how awesome\
  \ it is...\nThis is the story when I first went to Rajasthan, India..\nTotally new\
  \ experiences, different people with various tradition and cloting, \nExcited about\
  \ the trip, i came from my 11th exam and started packing my stuff, the bus was at\
  \ 11 at night, left home with blessing and waited 2 hour for bus, Gujarat seemed\
  \ a easy way but then it took us 8 hours untill we reach our friends home, as i\
  \ was imagining a desert landscape but has some Greenery and river \nFirst thing\
  \ came in my mind was swimming in river \nWe did that, but after 2 days..\nFirst\
  \ day meal was curd and roti.. \nFrom we sneaked out for the purpose we came that\
  \ is going Ajmer.. \nWe went Chittorgarh and then Ajmer...\nCame back to village\
  \ and then back to our home..."
